00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.790
And you'll, hopefully,
get that message

00:01:20.790 --> 00:01:23.190
when we get to that
part of the talk.

00:01:23.190 --> 00:01:26.750
And as a side note, we'll
have a little diversion.

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:28.850
So mostly, I do
evolutionary genetics.

00:01:28.850 --> 00:01:31.410
And I'm interested in
